        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Rebar juts from the frozen earth like rusty bones. Building materials are piled in chaotic heaps. Further back, rows of cold-weather tents dot the ice plain, a sight no better than the shacks they once lived in while working on ships.'}"
